
1-1. /hypercloud-operator/_yaml_Install/1.initialization.yaml 실행

1-2. HyperCloud CRDs Definition Yaml 적용
	- Auth/UserCRD.yaml
	- Auth/TokenCRD.yaml
	- Auth/ClientCRD.yaml
	- Claim/NamespaceClaimCRD.yaml
	- Claim/ResourceQuotaClaimCRD.yaml
	- Claim/RoleBindingClaimCRD.yaml
	- Registry/RegistryCRD.yaml
	- Registry/ImageCRD.yaml
	- Template/TemplateCRD_v1beta1.yaml
	- Template/TemplateInstanceCRD_v1beta1.yaml

2. /hypercloud-operator/_yaml_Install/2.mysql-settings.yaml 실행

3. /hypercloud-operator/_yaml_Install/3.mysql-create.yaml 실행

4. /hypercloud-operator/_yaml_Install/4.hypercloud4-operator.yaml 실행

5. /hypercloud-operator/_yaml_Install/5.secret-watcher.yaml 실행

6. /hypercloud-operator/_yaml_Install/6.default-auth-object-init.yaml 실행

7. authenticate webhook 설정
    - webhook-config 에 HYPERCLOUD_IP 치환
    - /etc/kubernetes/pki directory 에 webhook-config 복사
	- kube api-server manifest 설정에 아래 문구 추가
	- "--authentication-token-webhook-config-file=/etc/kubernetes/pki/webhook-config"
